title: Big Dot of Happiness Feliz Navidad - Holiday and Spanish Christmas Party Letter Banner Decoration - 36 Banner Cutouts and Feliz Navidad Banner Letters
features: Spanish Christmas Letter Banner Decoration INCLUDES Feliz Navidad letters, 36 banner pennant pieces and cord for hanging. Spanish Christmas banner look great at any venue!

VARIETY OF DESIGNS & SIZES! Feliz Navidad Letter Banner features coordinating pennant pieces and script letters. Decorate your event with 9 large triangle pennants (6.25” x 7.5”); 9 circle pennants (3.75” x 3.75”); 18 small triangle pennants (3.25” x 2”); and Feliz Navidad letters in script style lettering. Easily string them together with the included 10 yards of satin cording.

HISPANIC CHRISTMAS DECORATIONS: A Spanish Christmas Bunting Banner is an easy way to decorate for your party and bring your Feliz Navidad theme to life. Hang at the entrance of your holiday or Spanish Christmas party, over the food table or candy buffet, and even by the gift table.

PREMIUM SPANISH MERRY CHRISTMAS SUPPLIES: Feliz Navidad Letter Banner is professionally printed on sturdy cardstock paper. Each pennant is individually inspected then carefully packaged by hand. Feliz Navidad letter banners require some easy assembly. Simply string the cord through the holes on each letter piece and add triangle and circle pennants to complete the banner. Create multiple rows by cutting the cord to your desired length or hang as one long banner.
MADE IN THE USA: Feliz Navidad - Holiday or Spanish Christmas Party Letter Banner Decoration is designed and manufactured at our Wisconsin facility.
description: Greet your party guests with an impressive Spanish Christmas banner. Feliz Navidad Letter Banner Decoration is an eye-catching way to decorate for any Spanish Christmas. The variety of pennant designs and shapes paired with the Feliz Navidad script letters will look great at any venue. Simply string the script letters onto the included cording and then add the pennant shapes in any order your wish. Hang as one large banner or cut into different lengths and display in multiple rows. Letter banner decorations are an easy-to-use party supply for your celebration.
